title: Everything You Need to Know About San Francisco's Chase Center | San Francisco Travel
snippet: The Chase Center is a multi-purpose complex boasting arena seating capacity of 18,064, and the largest scoreboard in the NBA. There are a number of VIP seating options, including mid-level theater boxes and lounges on the lower levels.
